    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Sheet glass in which wire mesh is enclosed as a safety measure: when the glass is fractured the pieces are held together by the wire.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
